OL,3,CTreasury considered ending free museum
OL,4,Centry ahead of 2025 budget
OL,6,FThe Treasury was considering ending
OL,7,Ffree entry to museums and galleries as
OL,8,Fpart of spending cuts in the November
OL,9,F2025 budget, ITV News understands.
OL,11,FThe plans - which could have saved up
OL,12,Fto #480m from the annual Department
OL,13,Ffor Culture Media and Sport (DCMS)
OL,14,Fbudget - were eventually scrapped
OL,15,Fafter strong pushback from DCMS
OL,16,Fministers.
