OL,6,FThree senior sources told ITV News and
OL,7,FLBC that Treasury officials tried to
OL,8,Fend free museum and gallery entry for
OL,9,Fforeign nationals. Ending the benefit
OL,10,Ffor UK nationals was also modelled and
OL,11,Fconsidered.
OL,13,FFree entry to permanent exhibitions at
OL,14,Fmany of the UK's top museums and art
OL,15,Fgalleries was introduced in 2001.
