OL,6,FSharon Heal, Director at The Museums
OL,7,FAssociation, which represents two
OL,8,Fthousand UK museums, said: "We
OL,9,Fstrongly support free entry to
OL,10,Fnational museums and believe it has
OL,11,Fbeen a major cultural policy success
OL,12,Fwhich delivers a huge range of
OL,13,Fcultural, learning and economic
OL,14,Fbenefits.
OL,16,F"Admission charges for international
OL,17,Fvisitors could also cause reputational
OL,18,Fdamage for the UK which would likely
OL,19,Fimpact tourism and affect other
OL,20,Fsectors like retail and hospitality."
