OL,6,FMuseums in many other major cities
OL,7,Faround the world charge for entry. The
OL,8,FLouvre in Paris charges visitors up to
OL,9,FE32 (#28) for entry, while the Vatican
OL,10,FMuseum charges around E20 (#17).
OL,12,FThe Chancellor, Rachel Reeves, was
OL,13,Funder pressure to raise money in last
OL,14,Fyear's budget to pay for government
OL,15,Fpolicy reversals on welfare spending,
OL,16,Fthe abolition of the two-child benefit
OL,17,Fcap and increase fiscal headroom.
